<item>
<title>[SSTMAEM2U-16] SST for Bakong on MAE</title>
<link>https://jira.maybank.com.my/browse/SSTMAEM2U-16</link>
<project id="20509" key="SSTMAEM2U">MBB - SST on MAE and M2U</project>
<description><p>To introduce SST under the MAE screen as per below :</p> <div class='table-wrap'> <table class='confluenceTable'><tbody> <tr> <th class='confluenceTh'>Transaction initiation</th> <th class='confluenceTh'>Overseas Transfer type</th> <th class='confluenceTh'>Tool tip</th> </tr> <tr> <td class='confluenceTd'><span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1407819/1407819_image-2025-07-30-16-10-37-380.png" height="247" width="101" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span>  </td> <td class='confluenceTd'><span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1601559/1601559_image-2025-12-22-10-43-23-304.png" height="613" width="212" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span></td> <td class='confluenceTd'><span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1564306/1564306_image-2025-11-17-16-41-18-505.png" height="323" width="149" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span></td> </tr> <tr> <td class='confluenceTd'>1) Customer to login MAE using thier login credential and password<br/> 2) Customer to proceed with <br/> Transfer &gt; Overseas &gt; New / Fav transfer <br/> 3) The handling is as per BAU with no changes </td> <td class='confluenceTd'>1) Customer will then input the amount and select the currency to proceed<br/> 2) Titles with selection will be shown on the screen for customer selection<br/>  <br/> <b>New Business Requirement</b><br/> a) To update the below to include <b>"(Includes 8% SST)" only if there is already a charges</b> - Service Fees  <ul class="alternate" type="square"> <li>Agent/ Beneficiay Bank fees <br/> b) If there is <b>NO charges applies</b>, the below will not have any changes and follow as per <b>BAU</b>.</li> <li>Service Fees </li> <li>Agent/ Beneficiay Bank fees <br/> c) The "Transfer" amount will add in the 8% SST also<br/> d) The total chages will be getting from DCC as per existing maintenance <br/>  </li> <li><font color="#de350b">Technical Changes</font><br/> <font color="#de350b"> 1. Create new feature flag for SST in DCC</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">2. Maintain SST amount and percentage in DCC</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">3. Add description for SST at the front end</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">4. Update tooltip content</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">5. Update Total Amount calculation to be inclusive of SST amount</font></li> </ul> </td> <th class='confluenceTh'><b>New Business Requirement</b><br/> To updated the tool tip for "AGENT/BENEFICIARY BANK FEE"<br/>  <br/> <font color="#de350b">If an agent/beneficiary bank fee is applicable, the fee (inclusive of 8% SST) will be paid from your local accounts during the transfer details later.</font></th> </tr> <tr> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <th class='confluenceTh'> </th> </tr> </tbody></table> </div> <p> </p> <div class='table-wrap'> <table class='confluenceTable'><tbody> <tr> <th class='confluenceTh'>Transaction Flow</th> <th class='confluenceTh'>Confirmation page </th> <th class='confluenceTh'>S2U screen</th> <th class='confluenceTh'>Receipt page</th> <th class='confluenceTh'>Statement/ M2U history/ M2U transaction history </th> </tr> <tr> <td class='confluenceTd'><span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1407849/1407849_image-2025-07-31-09-16-41-703.png" height="398" width="184" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span></td> <td class='confluenceTd'>  <span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1407850/1407850_image-2025-07-31-09-16-55-086.png" height="338" width="150" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span><br/>  <br/>  <br/> <span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1508920/1508920_image-2025-10-03-09-52-00-428.png" height="346" width="152" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span></td> <td class='confluenceTd'><span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1417637/1417637_image-2025-08-05-14-37-09-213.png" height="268" width="121" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span></td> <td class='confluenceTd'><span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1508922/1508922_image-2025-10-03-09-52-30-696.png" height="358" width="131" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span></td> <td class='confluenceTd'>Phase 1<br/> <span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1601567/1601567_image-2025-12-22-10-44-41-751.png" height="391" width="160" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span><br/>  <br/> <span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1601568/1601568_image-2025-12-22-10-44-58-186.png" height="430" width="158" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span><br/>  <br/>  <br/>  <br/>  <br/> Phase 2<br/> <span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1407828/1407828_image-2025-07-30-16-15-55-054.png" height="387" width="142" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span><span class="image-wrap" style=""><img src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1407827/1407827_image-2025-07-30-16-15-40-395.png" height="346" width="142" style="border: 0px solid black" /></span><br/>  <br/>  <br/> Transaction History is based on the file <br/> <span class="nobr"><a href="https://jira.maybank.com.my/secure/attachment/1546598/1546598_Transaction+History_SST+Updated.xlsx" title="Transaction History_SST Updated.xlsx attached to SSTMAEM2U-16">Transaction History_SST Updated.xlsx<sup><img class="rendericon" src="https://jira.maybank.com.my/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif" height="7" width="7" align="absmiddle" alt="" border="0"/></sup></a></span></td> </tr> <tr> <td class='confluenceTd'>1) Customer to input all the field as per BAU today with no changes </td> <td class='confluenceTd'>1) All the information poulated is as per customer's input<br/> 2) The handling of all the CTA will not have any changes and it is as per BAU<br/>  <br/> <b>New Business Requirement</b><br/> a) To introduce the field in the screen <b>(Includes 8% SST)" if there is charges applies</b> <br/> <font color="#de350b">i) Principal </font><br/> <font color="#de350b">ii) Total Amount (<em>Principal + Service Fee + -Agent Fee + Service Fee SST + Agent Fee SST</em>)</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">iii) Service Fee</font><font color="#de350b">iv)8% SST on Service Fee (*Newly added)</font><font color="#de350b">v) Agent Fee</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">vi) 8% SST on Agent Fee (*Newly added)</font><br/> b) If there is <b>NO charges applies</b>, the below will not have any changes and follow as per <b>BAU</b>. - Service Fees  - Agent/ Beneficiay Bank fees<br/>  <br/> <font color="#de350b">Technical Changes</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">1. Add description for SST at the front end</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">2. To show new lines for Agent Fee SST and Service Fee SST</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">3. Update Total Amount calculation to be inclusive of SST amount</font></td> <td class='confluenceTd'>1) The handling will be as per BAU which total amount to reflect the total SSt<br/>  <br/> <b>New Business Requirement</b><br/> a) <font color="#de350b">To reflect the total amount the screen </font><b><font color="#de350b">(Includes 8% SST)"</font></b> <b>if there is charges applies</b> <br/> <font color="#de350b">i) Principal </font><br/> <font color="#de350b">ii) Total Amount (<em>Principal + Service Fee + -Agent Fee + Service Fee SST + Agent Fee SST</em>)</font><br/> <del><font color="#de350b">iii) Service Fee</font><font color="#de350b">iv)8% SST on Service Fee (*Newly added)</font><font color="#de350b">v) Agent Fee</font></del><br/> <del><font color="#de350b">vi) 8% SST on Agent Fee (*Newly added)</font></del> <br/> b) If there is <b>NO charges applies</b>, the below will not have any changes and follow as per <b>BAU</b>.<br/> -Service Fees <br/> -Agent/ Beneficiay Bank fees<br/> c) The "Transfer" amount will add in the 8% SST <br/> d) The total chages will be getting from DCC as per existing maintenance &#124;For each transaction with<br/> e) To remove the field of service charges and agent/ bene fees in S2U as it is repeated as per the total amount bracket<br/>  <br/> <font color="#de350b">Technical Changes<br/> 1. To implement v5 s2u - TESTING WILL REMAIN USING BAU FOR THE CURRENT VERSION</font><br/> <del><font color="#de350b">2. To remove existing field service fee and agent fee field -</font></del> <font color="#de350b">TO BE IMPLEMENTED IN V5</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">3. To include SSt amount in the transfer amount</font><br/> <del><font color="#de350b">4. To add SST description content</font></del></td> <td class='confluenceTd'>1) Customer then proceed with S2U and click PDF to generate receipt page<br/> 2) All the information will be as per customer's input<br/>  <br/>  <br/> <b>New Business Requirement</b><br/> a) To introduce the field in the screen <b>(Includes 8% SST)" if there is charges applies</b> <br/> <font color="#de350b">i) Principal </font><br/> <font color="#de350b">ii) Total Amount (<em>Principal + Service Fee + -Agent Fee + Service Fee SST + Agent Fee SST</em>)</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">iii) Service Fee</font><font color="#de350b">iv)8% SST on Service Fee (*Newly added)</font><font color="#de350b">v) Agent Fee</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">vi) 8% SST on Agent Fee (*Newly added)</font><br/> b) If there is <b>NO charges applies</b>, the below will not have any changes and follow as per <b>BAU</b>.<br/> -Service Fees <br/> -Agent/ Beneficiay Bank fees<br/> c) The "Transfer" amount will add in the 8% SST <br/> d) The total chages will be getting from DCC as per existing maintenance &#124;For each transaction with<br/>  <br/> <font color="#de350b">Technical Changes</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">1. To show new lines for Agent Fee SST and Service Fee SST</font><br/> <font color="#de350b">2. Update Total Amount calculation to be inclusive of SST amount</font><br/>  </td> <th class='confluenceTh'> &#124;<b>New Business Requirement</b><br/> a) Principal<br/> b) Service Fees<br/> c) Agent/ Beneficiay Bank fees<br/>  <br/> There will be <del>5</del> lines created which follow  <br/> <font color="#de350b"><del>i) Principal</del><br/> ii) Total Amount (<em>Principal + Service Fee + -Agent Fee + Service Fee SST + Agent Fee SST</em>)<br/> <del>iii) Service Feeiv)8% SST on Service Fee (*Newly added)v) Agent Fee</del><br/> <del>vi) 8% SST on Agent Fee (*Newly added)</del><br/> <br/> <br/> <del>Technical Changes</del><br/> <del>1. To show new lines for Agent Fee SST, Agent Fee SST, Service Fee, Service Fee SST and Principa</del></font><del>&#124;</del> </th> </tr> <tr> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <th class='confluenceTh'> </th> </tr> </tbody></table> </div> <p> <br/>  </p> <div class='table-wrap'> <table class='confluenceTable'><tbody> <tr> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> </tr> <tr> <th class='confluenceTh'> </th> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> <td class='confluenceTd'> </td> </tr> </tbody></table> </div> <p> </p> <p> </p></description>
